node.text:
Today @1rod1reelfishing and I are fishing in DC!!!
Fresh Waters is all about putting me in new and different fishing situations, to explore all the different ways people are enjoying their local water, in their own way. 

In this episode of Fresh Waters by Catch Co., I meet up with 1Rod1Reel Fishing, one of the most popular youtube fisherman ever. We visit the tidal basin in Washington D.C., fishing in front of the national monuments, on foot as we get on smallmouth, largemouth and try for other local species. Stay tuned as Mike and I have a fun day out on the water.
